Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…終於來到這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在都是職業棋士了 塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我刮目相看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是無視你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人生氣 不就是成績稍微好點兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是好一點點啦 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不但要追上他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是大手合的分組名單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一個對手是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一戰的對手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢今天來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才來電話了 樓裏都已經亂作一團了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢名人暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經被救護車送到醫院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(377,386)}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\be1\i1}sai的自白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近「神之一手」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 我們就以分先的形式下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的還有機會和他分先下一盤棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是哪家醫院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
