Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只是住院了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吧 去吧
